Package cinema

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DisplayStaffPage
    Boundary class between MainDisplayPage and StaffApp.
    DisplayUserPage
    Boundary class between MainDisplayPage and CustomerApp.
    MainDisplayPage
    Main boundary class between the user and the rest of the application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Calendar
    Calendar object that contains special dates that have special prices.
    Cinema
    Cinema object that contains details specific to each cinema.
    Cineplex
    Cineplex object that contains ArrayList of Cinema objects belonging to this cineplex, location of cineplex, unique cineplex ID.
    csvRW
    Contains methods that handles read and write to CSV.
    csvTester  
    CSVtoMovie
    Control class that converts all movies stored in database to Movie objects.
    CSVtoShowtime  
    Customer
    Customer object that contains unique customer ID, name, mobile number, email, and an ArrayList<Receipt> of receipts of previous bookings.
    CustomerApp
    An control class that will handle methods relating to the customer module.
    CustomerToCSV
    Control class to store Customer object into customerdatabase.
    Movie
    Movie object that contains movie details.
    MovieList  
    MovieToCSV
    Control class to store Movie object into moviedatabase.
    OverallRatingComparator
    Implements Comparator in order to sort Movie via review ratings
    Price
    Price object that determines the pricing of each ticket according to each criteria.
    Receipt
    Receipt object that contains ArrayList of Ticket objects bought in the same transaction by the same customer, TID, payment mode, and total amount paid.
    ReceiptToCSV
    Control class to store Receipt object into paymentdatabase.
    Review
    Review object that contains rating, comments, userID, and a unique reviewID.
    ReviewToCSV
    Control class to store Review object into reviewdatabase.
    Seat
    Seat object that contains x and y coordinates and occupied status for the seat.
    SeatingPlan
    Control class that takes in Showtime class and collects the necessary information to print the seating plan
    Showtime
    Showtime object that represent a particular instance of a movie showing at a particular time.
    Contains Cinema class that the cinema this showtime is located at belongs to, timing of showtime, seatingplan of the showtime, and list of Seat objects that are contained in this Showtime.
    ShowtimeToCSV  
    Staff
    Object containing staff username and password.
    StaffApp  
    StaffToCSV  
    Ticket
    Object containing attributes of tickets, such as showtime, movie title, unique ticket ID and price of ticket.
    TicketSalesComparator
    Implements Comparator in order to sort Movie via ticket sales.
    TicketToCSV
